  "texts": [
    "Single-nucleus RNA-seq reference from Jorstad et al.",
    "61 was subsetted to M1C cells and normalized in the same way as DART-FISH.",
    "Pax6 and Scng subclasses were removed since we did not design our probe set to target those.",
    "Average normalized counts (centroids) were computed for every other subclass in the \"within_area_subclass\" slot and all clusters of DART-FISH.",
    "To annotate the DART-FISH clusters at the class level (excitatory, inhibitory, non-neuronal), we first correlated each cluster to all singlenucleus subclasses, and assigned that cluster to the class of the most highly correlated subclass."
